Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,樓上的安全通訊簡報廳\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}in our secure comm and briefing facilities upstairs.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你，瑞特特工\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Well, thank you, agent ritter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体繁体\fad(0,500)\fs50\fsp8\be25\bord3\shad3\c&H82B7D4&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\t(\fs35)\pos(602,432)}导 演\N强·卡萨
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,奧德莉有消息嗎？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Have you heard anything from audrey?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,15分鐘前我和特勤局的人聯繫過\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I checked in on their secret service detail 15 minutes ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她和蕭還在談\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}She and jiao sim were still talking.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,鮑爾呢？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}What about bauer?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有鮑爾的消息，閣下\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Negative on bauer, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,情況如何，上將？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}What's our status, admiral?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,中方現在派了八隻兩棲部隊\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}The chinese now have eight amphibious landing groups{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,向我們在沖繩的基地前進\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}steaming toward our bases in okinawa.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,第一艘中方航母將在接下來半小時內\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}The first chinese carrier to reach the 12-mile limit{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抵達12英里界線\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}will be in the next half hour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体繁体\bord0\shad0\fsp5\fs35\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(850,270)}冲绳
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,屆時，我方第七艦隊已進入作戰準備狀態\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}At which point, the seventh fleet has standing orders to engage.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他們同時已命令己方核潛艇\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Also, they've ordered their nuclear armed submarines{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.90,0:07:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,升至三百英尺發射深度\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}to ascend to 300 feet firing depth.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,閣下，我們需要您批准\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Sir, we need your authorization{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.74,0:07:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,提高核戰備應答\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}to escalate our own nuclear readiness in response.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.71,0:07:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,將潛艇和發射井提到一級戒備\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Put our subs and silos on the highest alert.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看能不能接通魏主席\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}See if you can get President Wei on the line.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,女士，你還好麼？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Ma'am, are you okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧，親愛的？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Are you all right, love?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, I'm fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,能借用下電話麼？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Can I use your phone, please?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,當然可以\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Yes. Yes, of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,您哪位？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Who is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,傑克，是我\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Jack, it's me.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,克羅伊，你在哪？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Chloe, where are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我被程抓了，然後跳了車\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Cheng had me, I jumped out of his truck.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,艾德裏安死了\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Adrian's dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你收到了我信息\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}You got my message.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.86,0:08:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,知道他用裝置\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}You know he used the device{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,對中國航母發動了襲擊？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}to launch the attack on the Chinese carrier?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,知道，要是我活捉了程\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Yes, and if I capture Cheng alive{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,證明他有參與今天的襲擊\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}and can prove his involvement in today's attack{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也許就能讓中方放棄開戰\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}we might be able to get China to back down from war.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.86,0:08:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他在哪麼？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Do you know where he is?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他正準備乘貨船逃走\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}He's leaving on a cargo ship.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,貝爾切克會在碼頭與我碰面\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Belcheck's meeting me down at the docks.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.74,0:09:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能盲目行動\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}You can't go in there blind.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我在米爾斯伍德，離碼頭不遠，過來接我\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I'm at Millswood, not far from the docks. Come get me.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你調試通信設備\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I'll run comm for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,弄到衛星平面圖\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I'll get you satellites, schematics.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,克羅伊，我想這不行\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Chloe, I don't think that's a good idea.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.04,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,傑克，我知道你信不過我\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Jack, I know you don't trust me.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,艾德裏安騙了我\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Adrian lied to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我錯在不該信他\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}The only thing I did wrong was to believe him.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.38,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託，讓我將功補過\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Please, let me make this right.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪條街，我來接你\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Give me your cross streets, I'll pick you up.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,魏主席隨時可以通話\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}President Wei, whenever you're ready.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,開始吧\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Go.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,主席閣下\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Mr. President.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Forgive me for being blunt.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.27,0:09:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,貴方海軍正駛向沖繩\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}You've got your navy heading toward Okinawa{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.24,0:09:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我方第七艦隊也準備戒防\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}which our seventh fleet is ready to defend.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但避免熱戰才符合雙方利益\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}But it's in both our interests to avoid a shooting war.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是在我們雙方\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Especially with both our countries{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,高度核戰備的情況下\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}at a high level of nuclear readiness.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是你們尋釁\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}The destruction of our carrier{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,擊沉我方航母，殺死我們士兵\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}and the deaths of our soldiers is a provocation.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.45,0:09:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我軍必要做出回應\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Our military must respond.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們派出特工\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}We have agents in the field{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,正在追捕程志\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}in the process of apprehending Cheng Zhi.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這是事實\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}While that's happening{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.60,0:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我誠心請求您出於善意\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I'm asking you, as a gesture of good faith{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.30,0:10:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,停止海軍前進\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}to halt your naval advance.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我們軍隊官方認定\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Our military's official position{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.77,0:10:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,程已經死了\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}is that Cheng is dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,除非有其他證據\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Myself and my allies in the Politburo{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.44,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我和中共政治局的同黨們，只能這樣相信\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}must accept this is true, unless proven otherwise.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,您已說得夠清楚了，主席閣下\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}You've made yourself clear, Mr. President.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.28,0:10:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也把話講明白\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Let me make myself clear.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.18,0:10:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦您的軍隊越過沖繩外圍12英里界限…\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Once your forces cross the 12-mile limit outside of Okinawa...{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.62,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就開戰\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}We will fight.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你的人上船，別在這礙眼\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Get your men on board and out of sight.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.80,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,十五分鐘後離港\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}We are scheduled to depart in 15 minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,能再快點麼？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Is there a way to expedite this?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.48,0:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這會引起不必要的關注\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}That would draw scrutiny neither of us want.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正大黑繁体\bord0\shad0\fsp5\fs50\c&HDDDEDB&\pos(640,545)}上船，开始防卫阵地
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,克羅伊，上車\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Chloe, get in.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼了？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}What the hell happened?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.03,0:11:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好麼？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}You okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.20,0:11:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，沒事\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, I'm fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.54,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,為了擺脫程我被撞了\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I got banged up getting away from Cheng.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.87,0:11:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我們時間不多\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}We don't have a lot of time.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,路上再解釋\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I'll explain everything while we drive.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.51,0:11:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你的通信設備呢？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Where is your communications setup?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,後座行李箱裏\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}The trunk in the backseat.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.78,0:11:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,克羅伊，你為什麼破解遙控裝置後\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Chloe, I need to know why you were with Adrian Cross{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.05,0:11:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去找了艾德裏安·克羅斯\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}when you took the override device.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.82,0:11:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,傑克，我試圖把裝置拿回來\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Jack, I tried to get the device from Adrian{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.54,0:11:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但他有槍\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}but he had a gun.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.91,0:11:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們隨後返回基地，程卻在那等著\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}We got back to the base and Cheng was waiting.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.36,0:11:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,艾德裏安不是我想的那種人\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Adrian wasn't who I thought he was.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他愚弄了我\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}He manipulated me{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.10,0:11:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,利用我的知識開發了這個裝置\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}and he used my knowledge to create the device.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我也難辭其咎\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}So, this is partly my fault.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才決定幫你\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}That's why I need to help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.04,0:11:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我得盡力彌補\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I need to try to make this right.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看你吧\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}It's up to you.{\r}
