Dialogue: 1,0:33:34.57,0:33:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是鮑爾\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}This is Bauer.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:33:39.25,0:33:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Who is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:33:44.85,0:33:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,時間？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}When?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:33:47.89,0:33:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,地點？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Where?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:33:51.36,0:33:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Understood.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:33:55.93,0:33:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我會到的，你安排吧\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I'll be there. Just set it up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.95,0:34:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体繁体\fad(300,500)\fs60\be2\fsp8\bord2\shad2\c&H87BCDC&\pos(640,585)}12小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:34:24.30,0:34:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,埃裏克\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Erik.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:34:26.33,0:34:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的行動後報告\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}It's my after-action report.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:34:33.50,0:34:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,說真的…\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Look...{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:34:35.11,0:34:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,奧德莉的事\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}What happened to Audrey{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:34:36.77,0:34:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,並不是你的錯\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}it wasn't your fault.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:34:40.50,0:34:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,外勤工作變數太多\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Field work is not an exact science.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:34:42.03,0:34:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可能預料到\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}There's no way you could have known{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:34:43.50,0:34:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,程還會有第二個殺手\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}that Cheng had a second shooter.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:34:45.54,0:34:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我…這我明白\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah, I, uh... I realize that.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:35:43.89,0:35:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,遵總統命令\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Per the president's orders{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:35:45.56,0:35:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會護送你去萊肯希思\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}these men are going to escort you to Lakenheath{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:35:47.93,0:35:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裏會有架軍用運輸機送你回國\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}where a military transport will take you back to the States.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:35:58.31,0:36:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,總統怎麼樣了？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}How is the president?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:04.95,0:36:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我們說話這會兒，總統正在登上空軍一號\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}The president is boarding Air Force One as we speak.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:39.95,0:36:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯，我深表遺憾\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}James, you have my deepest sympathy.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:42.65,0:36:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是無法想像你現在的痛苦\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I can't even imagine what you're going through.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:45.79,0:36:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你，阿拉斯泰爾\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you, Alastair.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:48.69,0:36:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都是一個很好的朋友\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}You've been a good friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:51.13,0:36:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有任何我能做的事情，任何事…\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}If there's anything I can do, anything at all...{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:55.16,0:36:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有，你無能為力\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}No, there's nothing you can do.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:36:59.83,0:37:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人都無能為力\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Nothing anyone can do.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:07.54,0:37:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們啟程來倫敦的前一天\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}The day before we left for London,{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:09.31,0:37:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我坐在我的辦公室裏\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I was sitting in my office{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:12.65,0:37:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我桌子上一張美麗的女人的照片\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}looking at a picture on my desk of a beautiful woman.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:16.32,0:37:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我就那麼一直看著\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I kept staring at it.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:18.39,0:37:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,從我當政那天起\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}It's been on my desk{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:19.89,0:37:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它就在我桌子上擺著\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}since my first day in office.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:23.49,0:37:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我認識那個女人\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}And I knew that I knew that woman.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:27.56,0:37:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可我就是想不起來她的名字\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}But I couldn't think of her name.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:32.07,0:37:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,10秒鐘，15秒鐘，然後，忽地一下\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Ten seconds, 15 seconds go by, then, poof.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:37.41,0:37:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,驀然記起\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Pops into my head.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:40.68,0:37:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是奧德莉啊\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}It was Audrey.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:45.68,0:37:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I'm so sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:50.72,0:37:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我會記不起今天發生的任何事\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I won't remember anything that happens today.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:37:57.09,0:38:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我會記不起以往所有事，罷了\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I won't remember anything that happens, period.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:38:03.43,0:38:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我會記不起我曾有個女兒，如是慘死\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I won't remember that I had a daughter that died in such a horrible fashion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.94,0:39:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正黑体繁体\fad(300,500)\fs60\be5\fsp8\bord2\shad2\c&H87BCDC&\pos(640,585)}伦敦郊外
Dialogue: 1,0:39:50.81,0:39:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定要這麼做嗎？\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Are you sure you want to do this?{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:39:53.64,0:39:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:40:35.72,0:40:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她先走！\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}She walks first!{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:00.04,0:41:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,傑克，你不用這麼做的\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Jack, you don't have to do this.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:02.28,0:41:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你該回家了\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}It's time for you to go home.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:05.92,0:41:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前說的是對的\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}You were right about what you said earlier.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:08.78,0:41:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我最好的朋友\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}About being my best friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:16.89,0:41:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:21.13,0:41:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有時間就去看看我的家人\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Look in on my family when you can.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:22.96,0:41:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Go.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:24.73,0:41:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,走\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Go.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:37.45,0:41:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你言出必行\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I've taken you at your word.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:39.61,0:41:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但若你膽敢食言\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}But if you're lying to me{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:41.62,0:41:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她或者我的家人出了任何事\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}if anything happens to her or my family{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:43.92,0:41:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我會讓你整個世界分崩離析\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}your entire world will come apart{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:45.92,0:41:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而你防不勝防\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}and you will never see it coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:49.09,0:41:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要的只是你，鮑爾先生\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}We just want you, Mr. Bauer.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:41:52.13,0:41:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,僅此而已\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}That's all we ever wanted.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:42:01.50,0:42:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我想說你會喜歡莫斯科的\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}I would say you're going to enjoy Moscow{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:42:05.14,0:42:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但你也知道那是假話\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}but you'd know I was lying.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:42:37.14,0:42:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,到車裏去\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Go to the car.{\r}
Dialogue: 1,0:42:38.87,0:42:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,去\N{\fnArial\fs38\fsp0\1c&H0080FF&}Go.{\r}
